      <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333;">For over 30 years, the nation of Cuba has treated over 5,000 lung cancer patients at a cost of only $1 per treatment. Using a unique form of treatment called immunotherapy, the vaccine, CimaVax, supercharges the patient’s own immune system to combat the disease - with little to no known side effects.
