    <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333;">In the coming year, nearly 2 million new people will develop lung cancer, and over a quarter of a million will die - but it doesn’t have to be that way.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333;">We believe that no one should suffer or prematurely die from a disease that can be managed and treated, no matter your condition - and we're here to help.
